Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
extract_metal_density(25.10)                      extract_metal_density(25.10)

Name
       extract_metal_density - Specifies to extract the metal density informa-
       tion

Syntax
       extract_metal_density

       -help

       Specifies  to extract the metal density information. The command gener-
       ates the Voltus Thermal Model (VTM) for Celsius only if you do not want
       to include power information. Before specifying this command,  use  the
       set_metal_density_options  command to set the parameters for extracting
       the metal density information.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs the command usage and a brief description about the com-
              mand parameters.

Examples
              * The following command specifies to run extract metal density:

                extract_metal_density

Related Information
              * set_metal_density_options

